---
alwaysApply: true
---

Phased Rollouts: All systems must be deployed incrementally (staging → internal beta → partial live → full launch) to reduce risk.

Feedback Loops: Continuous tracking of user interactions, conversions, and refunds must feed into AI and operational optimizations.

Feature Flags: New functions or updates must always be wrapped in feature flags to allow controlled releases.

Documentation: Every system, workflow, and AI update must be fully documented for team onboarding and compliance.
